data.description: So much potential. 20+ acres. Rental Income from duplex. Each unit has 2 bdrms, 1 bath. Ready to build your dream home. Approved septic design and all utilities are at the property. Single wide mobile home which must be removed when new home is built. Sellers have an approved rambler plan w/ bonus room above garage. Great pasture land, 2 barns & silo. HUGE shop & a 2 car detached garage. Enjoy income from rentals. Terrific mother in law set up. Build your dream house. Great opportunity for someone! 11.8+ acres come with home, additional 10+ acres are on a 10 year lease. Price reduced to $699,950
